            "text_mHDp8L": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We aim to set a new benchmark for those that also believe that, not only can we work in harmony with nature, you can give back more than you take. Our pioneering and rigorous commitment to regenerative farming techniques is captured in La Marca De Cala Falcó. </p><p>As we encourage more people to walk our path and follow 'The Cala Falcó Way’ we envision our marque as a recognised symbol for regenerative farming practices. You will find our marque on all Cala Falcó products and the product of partners who have achieved the exemplary standard we hold ourselves accountable to.</p>",
