            "text_DAmtY7": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We are one big happy family at Cala Falcó. From our founder to our farmers, from the pickers to the botanical microbiologists, everyone plays a crucial role in delivering our vision to heal the land. Our friends from Estel de Llevant, founded in 1997, supports people with mental health conditions through training, employment, and inclusion programs. We proudly partner with them in a shared commitment to community and social impact, collaborating on essential oil distillation and welcoming their support during harvests in Cala Falcó.</p>",
